{"tid":1171835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又贏！擬以關愛基金為劏房戶提供津貼 用以購買傢俬、家居改善","createTime":"2019-05-26T04:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T08:38:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8739695ffb3e5e0218c54e62d4af33e6a92a06b","tid":1171835,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"勞工及福利局局長羅致光今日（26日）發表網誌，稱計劃透過關愛基金推行一個新項目，為居於劏房的低收入住戶提供一筆過津貼，進行簡單家居改善／維修、購買傢俬等服務，以改善他們的家居環境。<br />\n羅致光指出，相關項目將由社會福利署負責推行，社聯將負責統籌。由於預算高達2.9億元，故會根據程序，先聽取立法會意見，及後將會提交給關愛基金專責小組及扶貧委員會審批，料明年第二季開始推行，為期兩年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/333206/羅致光-擬以關愛基金為劏房戶提供一筆過津貼-為期兩年\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F333206%2F%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E6%93%AC%E4%BB%A5%E9%97%9C%E6%84%9B%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E7%82%BA%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%86%E9%81%8E%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC-%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%9F%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFDUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=9e0f6372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/333206/羅致光-擬以關愛基金為劏房戶提供一筆過津貼-為期兩年</a>"},{"pid":"c700cb07507220cac702c017cf0abaecc7145c60","tid":1171835,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cc7163da7fd5c3ba30acdab80545d8657e71e8","tid":1171835,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:02:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">操你妈</span></span>"},{"pid":"38b3d1996a45ae93d648ebc597995328bcc7b931","tid":1171835,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"有錢身痕"},{"pid":"ad0fdb253f7923668f31e88144b3b02cccbaf92e","tid":1171835,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"幹你娘